# Crafting System Guide

Welcome to the Crafting System Guide! This guide will help you understand how to create items using blueprints, workbenches, and various tools. Crafting is an essential part of survival in the wasteland.

Let’s dive into the details!

## Crafting Basics

Crafting is the process of creating items using blueprints, resources, and tools. Each blueprint specifies the required materials, tools, and workbench needed to craft the item. Here’s how it works:

1. Blueprints: Blueprints are the instructions for crafting. They specify the required resources, tools, and workbench type. Without a blueprint, you cannot craft an item.
